com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.filters

Class TokenRegexFilterImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.filters.AbstractRegexFilter
      • com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.filters.TokenRegexFilterImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeedsTalismaneSession, TokenFilter, TokenRegexFilter

    public class TokenRegexFilterImpl
extends AbstractRegexFilter
    A default implementation for token regex filters. It tokenises the matched group as a single separate token, and offers the possibility of a replacement string to replace the token text. See RegexUtils.getReplacement(String, String, Matcher) for handling of the replacement string.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
